Detectives Hunt Gangland Killers | The 4 Points | Crime Drama Movie

Growing up in The 4 Points area of Los Angeles, a two man LAPD task force are assigned to address the rising violence in The 4 Points. Things get dark as they investigate the most recent gangland murders.

2025 | Stars: Dustin Harnish, Dominique Marsell, Dorien Wilson
